Re: Sore ...
by takiras » Sun 10.17.2010 9:59 am それからいいですか - I'd guess the それ here would be referring to previously-mentioned things, so it might be literally 'Is that OK?'I totally agree with furrykef on the second sentence.
青い空を共に行こうよ[fb][last.fm][twitter]
