Re: Sore ...
by Hyperworm » Sun 10.17.2010 10:08 am 「それから、」can mean "also", so it might be that.It could mean a range of different things depending on the context though.Provide more context if you want better answers. fun translation snippets | need something translated?BTC@1KMZXgoWiDshQis5Z7feCx8jaiP4QAB2ks
